{"tid":2143443,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［待FC] 萬達用10億美元起樓 2.7億賤賣俾芝加哥巿長家族 後者用棟樓嚟做投資移民生意?!","createTime":"2020-08-07T05:53:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-07T06:24:37.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0dc00c6b497dc55e2bd068010ab7beaf849519e3","tid":2143443,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T05:53:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/xunlongji/status/1291598391613554688?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fxunlongji%2Fstatus%2F1291598391613554688%3Fs%3D21&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLBVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=e7700c6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fxunlongji%2Fstatus%2F1291598391613554688%3Fs%3D21&h=e37646dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/xunlongji/status/1291598391613554688?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4cqg9yx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4cqg9yx.jpg&h=25aed19e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【大紀元2016年10月27日訊】....芝加哥太陽報披露，芝加哥前市長戴利（Richard M。 Daley）和兒子正向聯邦政府申請EB-5投資項目，吸引中國人投資，這預計將為他們賺得1500萬美元的手續費。　　<br />\n<br />\n戴利從1989年至2011年擔任芝加哥市長，是芝加哥任職最長的市長。卸任後，他和兒子派翠克（Patrick Daley）成立了特爾投資顧問公司（Tur Partners），去<strong>年9月22日向國土安全局申請成立EB-5項目，在芝加哥市中心建設萬達大廈（Vista Tower），這樣他們可以向外國人簽發EB-5投資移民簽證暨綠卡，進而換取每人50萬美金的投資。 　　<br />\n<br />\n戴利父子希望能吸引到300名外國投資客，多數將可能是中國人。每個人除了投資50萬美元獲得EB-5投資移民綠卡外，還需支付5萬美金的手續費。這樣特爾公司可籌得1億5千萬美元的投資，以及賺得1500萬美元的手續費。 　　</strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><br />\n戴利父子和萬達大廈<br />\n<br />\n戴利父子將把這1億5千萬美元借給芝加哥的地產開發商麥哲倫開發集團（Magellan Development Group），麥哲倫是萬達大廈的建商。 </span></strong>　　<br />\n<br />\n申請材料中說，投資將用於在195 N. Columbus Dr上建高樓，當中有一頁材料又提到383 E. Wacker Dr，這正是萬達大廈的建址。萬達大廈耗資10億美金，大部分由中國的萬達集團提供，麥哲倫也出資一部分。　　<br />\n<br />\n特爾公司申請EB-5項目的$6230的支票來自麥哲倫公司。而戴利的兒子派翠克說他們與萬達大樓的建設無關。 　<br />\n<br />\n　太陽報詢問，為什麼申請材料中提到要建設兩座高樓，一座是正在興建的萬達大廈，一座還沒動工，代號為Site O。麥哲倫公司主席David Carlins稱，EB-5的融資還沒最後確定要進入哪一個項目，當然萬達大廈已經很有進展，更有可能使用EB-5資金。　　<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/16/10/26/n8433794.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fgb%2F16%2F10%2F26%2Fn8433794.htm&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLBVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=8d988367\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/gb/16/10/26/n8433794.htm</a><br />\n　　"},{"pid":"b0c4fecdce051176611a4270f4167235f4a1bb45","tid":2143443,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T05:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41e41f299e044c34ba6f02b68282b6d830854719","tid":2143443,"uid":42364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T05:59:30.000Z","msg":"咁樣又賣到二千張綠卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24b48dd6736590165619beae39944edb0901cd42","tid":2143443,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41e41f299e044c34ba6f02b68282b6d830854719","tid":2143443,"uid":42364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T05:59:30.000Z","msg":"咁樣又賣到二千張綠卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T06:05:50.000Z","msg":"每個家庭50萬美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f64aa6c39373bab0e32246d4f41fa8623def266","tid":2143443,"uid":42364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24b48dd6736590165619beae39944edb0901cd42","tid":2143443,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41e41f299e044c34ba6f02b68282b6d830854719","tid":2143443,"uid":42364,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T05:59:30.000Z","msg":"咁樣又賣到二千張綠卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T06:05:50.000Z","msg":"每個家庭50萬美元<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"